# License signing — never commit a private key or an issued customer license.
# The signing keypair lives OUTSIDE the repo (~/.roar-signing/); these patterns
# are a defensive net in case a tool is run from the repo directory.
*_private_key.pem
*private*.pem
roar_pro_*.json
roar_developer_*.json
roar_supporter_*.json
*roar_license*.json
roar_license.json

